    <h2>The Virtue App</h2>
    <p>The Virtue app lets you set time limits for distracting apps. If you exceed your limits, you lose money or go through mindful ad breaks. If you stay disciplined, you earn rewards and build better digital habits.</p>
    <p>Download Virtue from the <a href="#" target="_blank">Google Play Store</a>.</p>
